Modifications for Bughouse chess variant:
- Added piece drop move support (@-notation parsing)
- Extended FEN parser for piece reserves [NP] format
- Modified move validation to allow king capture rules
- Exposed attack square calculation functions for UI
- Renamed application from 'binbo' to 'binbo_bughouse'
- Updated API module from 'binbo' to 'binbo_bughouse'
